## ğŸ“¦ What Youâ€™ll Build

- Control your PC **mouse cursor** with a joystick  
- Use a rotary encoder to **scroll**  
- Press buttons to **left-click** and **right-click**  
- Connects via **Bluetooth**, no dongle or drivers needed!

