## ğŸ”Œ Circuit Wiring

### ğŸ•¹ï¸ Joystick â†’ ESP32

| Joystick Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|--------------|-----------|
| VRx          | GPIO 34   |
| VRy          | GPIO 35   |
| SW           | GPIO 25   |
| VCC          | 3.3V      |
| GND          | GND       |

### ğŸ” Rotary Encoder â†’ ESP32

| Encoder Pin | ESP32 Pin |
|-------------|-----------|
| CLK         | GPIO 18   |
| DT          | GPIO 19   |
| SW          | GPIO 21   |
| +           | 3.3V      |
| GND         | GND       |

> âš ï¸ **Use only 3.3V**, not 5V, to avoid damaging the ESP32.

